    <requiresclause>IsStrongIdLike&lt;TStrongId&gt;    </requiresclause>
    <briefdescription>
<para>A versioned handle for referencing entities in a registry. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>`EntityHandle` combines an entity ID with a version number and a domain-specific strong ID to provide safe, typed references to registered entities. The version ensures that handles to removed entities are detected as stale.</para>
<para><parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>TStrongId</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>A strong ID type carrying domain semantics.</para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
<simplesect kind="see"><para><ref refid="classhelios_1_1ecs_1_1EntityRegistry" kindref="compound">EntityRegistry</ref> </para>
</simplesect>
</para>
    </detaileddescription>
